posts.body:
@mcdev
i think IF it is not possible to allow people to clone hub by clicking a button on the merger site, it should be a priority to create some tutorial and link it from the merger site so even zeronet noobs has as easy as possible way to create new discussion board.

I am also missing some way to distribute all new images of a discussion board. Zeronet noob do not know there is such a possibility, there is no clickable link to the hub address, then one have to know the zero button in corner of the hub site has to be swiped to the left to open menu and find approptiate option to download all hub content (all current & future images of particular discussion board).
